<paragraph blockId="40.[151,1436,576,891]" pageId="40" pageNumber="491">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[199,298,649,675]" pageId="40" pageNumber="491">Habitat.</emphasis>
This species has been found in lotic habitats (creeks, streams and rivers), and in lentic habitats (ditches, marshes, pools, ponds, lakes and lagoons) including artificial channels and lakes (
<bibRefCitation author="Truxal, F. S." box="[1123,1266,685,711]" pageId="40" pageNumber="491" pagination="1 - 24" refId="ref58717" refString="Truxal, F. S. (1949) A study of the genus Martarega (Hemiptera, Notonectidae). Journal of the Kansas Entomological Society, 22, 1 - 24." type="journal article" year="1949">Truxal 1949</bibRefCitation>
; 
<bibRefCitation author="Nieser, N." box="[1279,1432,685,711]" pageId="40" pageNumber="491" pagination="71 - 93" refId="ref54845" refString="Nieser, N. (1970 a) Records of South American Notonectidae mainly from the Amazon-region. Studies on the Fauna of Suriname and other Guyanas, 12, 71 - 93." type="journal article" year="1970">Nieser 1970a</bibRefCitation>
, 
<bibRefCitation author="Nieser, N." box="[151,210,721,748]" pageId="40" pageNumber="491" pagination="1 - 310" refId="ref54944" refString="Nieser, N. (1975) The water bugs (Heteroptera: Nepomorpha) of the Guyana Region. Studies on the Fauna of Suriname and other Guyanas, 16, 1 - 310. https: // doi. org / 10.1007 / 978 - 94 - 017 - 7118 - 4 _ 1" type="journal article" year="1975">1975</bibRefCitation>
; 
<bibRefCitation author="Pereira, D. L. V. &amp; Melo, A. L." box="[222,461,721,747]" pageId="40" pageNumber="491" pagination="643 - 648" refId="ref55645" refString="Pereira, D. L. V. &amp; Melo, A. L. (2007) Aquatic and semiaquatic Heteroptera (Insecta) from Pitinga, Amazonas, Brazil. Acta Amazonica, 37, 643 - 648. https: // doi. org / 10.1590 / S 0044 - 59672007000400021" type="journal article" year="2007">Pereira &amp; Melo 2007</bibRefCitation>
; 
<bibRefCitation author="Barbosa, J. F. &amp; Ribeiro, J. R. I. &amp; Nessimian, J. L." box="[473,694,721,747]" pageId="40" pageNumber="491" pagination="1025 - 1057" refId="ref46841" refString="Barbosa, J. F., Ribeiro, J. R. I. &amp; Nessimian, J. L. (2012) A synopsis of Martarega White, 1879 (Insecta: Heteroptera: Notonectidae) occurring in the Brazilian Amazonia, with descriptions of three new species. Journal of Natural History, 46, 1025 - 1057. https: // doi. org / 10.1080 / 00222933.2011.651645" type="journal article" year="2012">
Barbosa 
<emphasis box="[572,628,721,747]" italics="true" pageId="40" pageNumber="491">et al.</emphasis>
2012
</bibRefCitation>
