<bibRefCitation author="Barbosa, J. F. &amp; Giehl, N. F. S." box="[705,962,721,747]" pageId="40" pageNumber="491" pagination="1152 - 1155" refId="ref46709" refString="Barbosa, J. F. &amp; Giehl, N. F. S. (2014) New distribution records of the genus Martarega White, 1879 (Hemiptera: Heteroptera: Notonectidae) in eastern Mato Grosso state, Brazil. Check List, 10 (5), 1152 - 1155. https: // doi. org / 10.15560 / 10.5.1152" type="journal article" year="2014">Barbosa &amp; Giehl 2014</bibRefCitation>
). This species has also been taken at lights and in a swimming pool (
<bibRefCitation author="Barbosa, J. F. &amp; Rodrigues, H. D. D." box="[436,749,757,783]" pageId="40" pageNumber="491" pagination="534 - 540" refId="ref46914" refString="Barbosa, J. F. &amp; Rodrigues, H. D. D. (2013) A new species of Martarega White, 1879, with new distributional records of Notonectidae (Hemiptera: Heteroptera: Nepomorpha) from Brazil. Zootaxa, 3682 (4), 534 - 540. https: // doi. org / 10.11646 / zootaxa. 3682.4.4" type="journal article" year="2013">Barbosa &amp; Rodrigues 2013</bibRefCitation>
