<subSubSection pageId="40" pageNumber="491" type="discussion">
<paragraph blockId="40.[151,1436,576,891]" pageId="40" pageNumber="491">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[199,313,829,855]" pageId="40" pageNumber="491">Remarks.</emphasis>
This is the first record of 
<taxonomicName authorityName="White" authorityYear="1879" box="[597,792,829,855]" class="Insecta" family="Notonectidae" genus="Martarega" kingdom="Animalia" order="Hemiptera" pageId="40" pageNumber="491" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="membranacea">
<emphasis box="[597,792,829,855]" italics="true" pageId="40" pageNumber="491">M. membranacea</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
from INR. This species was previously recorded from 
<collectingRegion country="Argentina" name="Corrientes" pageId="40" pageNumber="491">Corrientes Province</collectingRegion>
by 
<bibRefCitation author="Lopez Ruf, M. L. &amp; Mazzucconi, S. A. &amp; Bachmann, A. O." box="[371,634,865,891]" pageId="40" pageNumber="491" pagination="65 - 71" refId="ref52192" refString="Lopez Ruf, M. L., Mazzucconi, S. A. &amp; Bachmann, A. O. (2003) Heteroptera acuaticos y semiacuaticos del Parque Nacional Mburucuya (provincia de Corrientes, Argentina). Revista de la Sociedad Entomologica Argentina, 62 (1 - 2), 65 - 71." type="journal article" year="2003">
López Ruf 
<emphasis box="[497,553,865,891]" italics="true" pageId="40" pageNumber="491">et al.</emphasis>
(2003)
</bibRefCitation>
and 
<bibRefCitation author="Mazzucconi, S. A." box="[689,910,865,891]" pageId="40" pageNumber="491" pagination="209 - 221" refId="ref52493" refString="Mazzucconi, S. A. (2008) Notonectidae (Insecta: Hemiptera: Heteroptera). In: Claps, L. E., Debandi, G. &amp; Roig-Junent, S. (Dir.), Biodiversidad de Artropodos Argentinos 2. Sociedad Entomologica Argentina, Mendoza, pp. 209 - 221." type="book chapter" year="2008">Mazzucconi (2008)</bibRefCitation>
.
</paragraph>
